g, damaging or alienating, removing or disposing of their properties comprised in Singo Block}{\insrsid6623029\charrsid31649  293 Plot 47 Land at }{\insrsid788741\charrsid31649 M}{\insrsid6623029\charrsid31649 yanzi}{\insrsid4016719\charrsid31649 
